description:
This is a 12 minute workout called '10 Min Yoga Full Body Stretch' from the channel Yoga With Tim.
The workout falls under Flexibility/Yoga and Flexibility/Stretching.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Beginner fitness levels.
The workout has a The Zen Flow and The Reboot Workout vibe.
The technique difficulty is Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: This is an intermediate version of my 10 Min Yoga Full Body Stretch Routine.  The exercises in this routine when practiced regularly will help to improve your flexibility and strength for better full body mobility....
